---
const { id } = Astro.props;
---

<div id={id}></div>
<h2>MÅNEDENS KVINDE</h2>
<div class="container">
  <div class="col1">
    <img src="./img/luna_nobackg.webp" alt="luna" />
  </div>
  <div class="col2">
    <p class="kvinde">
      Luna <br />
      27 år <br />
      Danmark <br />
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2>MÅNEDENS KVINDE</h2>
<div class="container1">
  <div id="text">
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ipsum qui id
      natus aliquam modi sed vero accusamus sint, voluptas, placeat minus
      deserunt ad rerum pariatur eveniet. Iure, ratione! Vel, aut.
    </p>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Qui in temporibus
      sed quae nobis tempore commodi totam? Quo itaque maxime ipsa molestiae
      eveniet. Ea sint pariatur tempore iusto voluptate eaque.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div id="billede_con1_1">
    <img src="./img/clothing.jpg" alt="tøj" id="billede1_1" />
    <img src="./illustrationer/blaa.svg" alt="" id="billede1_2" />
    <img src="./img/symaskine.svg" alt="symaskine" id="billede1_3" />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="symaskine"></div>
<img src="./img/symaskine.svg" alt="symaskine" id="billede1_3" />
<style>
  h2 {
    margin-top: 70px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container > * {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .col1 img {
    width: 500px;
  }

  .container1 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
  #billede_con1_1 {
    grid-column: 2;
    height: 30em;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  #billede1_1 {
    z-index: 1;
    height: 70%;
    width: auto;
    position: absolute;
  }
  #billede1_2 {
    height: 100%;
    width: auto;
  }

  #billede1_3 {
    height: 30%;
    width: auto;
    z-index: 1;
    position: absolute;
    padding-right: 350px;
  }
</style>

